OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778695869
OL,3,CGiant mural dedicated to Stone Roses
OL,4,Cbassist painted on side of home town
OL,5,Cpub
OL,7,FA huge mural dedicated to a music
OL,8,Flegend has been painted onto the side
OL,9,Fof a pub in his home town.
OL,11,FThe giant tribute to Stone Roses
OL,12,Fmember Gary 'Mani' Mounfield, which
OL,13,Fdepicts him playing his bass guitar,
OL,14,Fhas been painted onto the wall of La
OL,15,FFardy pub on Oldham Road in his
OL,16,Fhometown of Failsworth, Greater
OL,17,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
