PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778695869
OL,3,CGiant mural dedicated to Stone Roses
OL,4,Cbassist painted on side of home town
OL,5,Cpub
OL,7,FArtist Pic.One.Art, who created the
OL,8,FOasis mural in Burnage, was
OL,9,Fcommissioned to the project and the
OL,10,Flocation was found by Mani's brother
OL,11,FGreg Mounfield.
OL,13,FThe lemon is a nod to The Stone Roses
OL,14,Fand the iconic artwork of his bandmate
OL,15,FJohn Squire, while the far side of the
OL,16,Fartwork depicts the Primal Scream
OL,17,FScreamadelic icon.
OL,19,FGreg said hundreds of fans have
OL,20,Fvisited the mural over the past few
OL,21,Fweeks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778695869
OL,3,CGiant mural dedicated to Stone Roses
OL,4,Cbassist painted on side of home town
OL,5,Cpub
OL,7,FHe said: "I've seen people from all
OL,8,Fover the world coming up here to pay
OL,9,Ftribute already.
OL,11,F"The amount of people turning up to
OL,12,Ftake pictures, and then popping into
OL,13,Fthe pub for a pint, it's just been
OL,14,Ffantastic."
OL,16,FFormer Happy Mondays singer Rowetta
OL,17,Fshared a picture taken at the mural,
OL,18,Fwith the caption: "Mani Forver".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
