PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778695869
OL,3,CGiant mural dedicated to Stone Roses
OL,4,Cbassist painted on side of home town
OL,5,Cpub
OL,7,FMani passed away aged 63 in November,
OL,8,Fof respiratory issues linked to a long-
OL,9,Fstanding lung condition.
OL,11,FHis death came almost two years to the
OL,12,Fday after losing his wife Imelda, who
OL,13,Fpassed away with cancer, aged 50, on
OL,14,F18 November 2023.
OL,16,FA community crowdfunder for the mural
OL,17,Fwas set up by GRIT Studios, with all
OL,18,Fof the money donated going Maggies
OL,19,FManchester - which supported Imelda
OL,20,Fduring her treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778695869
OL,3,CGiant mural dedicated to Stone Roses
OL,4,Cbassist painted on side of home town
OL,5,Cpub
OL,7,FThe idea for a permanent tribute came
OL,8,Fafter bandmate and Roses frontman Ian
OL,9,FBrown delivered a eulogy during his
OL,10,Ffuneral service at Manchester
OL,11,FCathedral in December.
OL,13,FIan stated he would love to see a "50-
OL,14,Ffoot gold statue" of Mani erected to
OL,15,Fcommemorate his life and career.
OL,17,FGreg is now planning a celebration
OL,18,Fevent to officially launch the mural
OL,19,Fin early June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
