OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778695869
OL,3,CGiant mural dedicated to Stone Roses
OL,4,Cbassist painted on side of home town
OL,5,Cpub
OL,7,FThe mural is expected to become a
OL,8,Fcultural landmark in north Manchester,
OL,9,Foffering fans and the local community
OL,10,Fa place to reflect and celebrate
OL,11,FMani's influence on music and culture.
OL,13,FListen to the ITV News entertainment
OL,14,Fpodcast, Unscripted
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
